body_html:
That looks like an issue in WinPython, please try looking through product forums of that tool.
This google search tells me a lot of users of this tool faced similar issues:
https://www.google.com/search?q=%22unable+to+install%22+winpython&oq=%22unable+to+install%22+winpython&aqs=chrome..69i64j46l3j69i57.1513j0j7&sourceid=chrome&ie=UTF-8

I will close this issue, as it is not a TF bug.
